    %% KServe - central serving hub
    KServe -->|autoscaling| Knative
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt| Istio
    vLLM -->|runtime for| KServe
    TGIS -->|runtime for| KServe
    MLServer -->|runtime for| KServe
    OVMS -->|runtime for| KServe
    CaikitRuntime -->|runtime for| KServe
    vLLMCPU -->|runtime for| KServe
    vLLMGaudi -->|runtime for| KServe
    vLLMROCm -->|runtime for| KServe
    vLLMSpyre -->|runtime for| KServe

    %% LLM Infrastructure
    EPP -->|scores and routes| vLLM
    KVCache -->|sidecar for| vLLM
    RoutingSidecar -->|sidecar for| vLLM
    llmd -->|orchestrates| EPP
    llmd -->|orchestrates| KVCache
    llmd -->|orchestrates| RoutingSidecar
    AIGW -->|ext-proc routing| EPP
    AIGW -->|NeMo guard| NeMo
    BatchGW -->|batch requests| vLLM
    WVA -->|autoscales| KServe

    %% MaaS integration
    MaaS -->|backend status| KServe
    MaaS -->|auth policies| Kuadrant

    %% Dashboard dependencies
    Dashboard -->|pipeline mgmt| DSP
    Dashboard -->|model serving| KServe
    Dashboard -->|model registry| ModelRegistry
    Dashboard -->|notebook mgmt| Notebooks
    Dashboard -->|evaluation UI| TrustyAIOp
    Dashboard -->|experiment tracking| MLflowOp
    Dashboard -->|model catalog| MaaS
    Dashboard -->|Llama Stack mgmt| LlamaStackDist

    %% Model controller
    ODHModelCtrl -->|routing for| KServe
    ODHModelCtrl -->|HTTPRoutes + AuthPolicy| Kuadrant

    %% Pipeline flows
    DSPO -->|deploys| ArgoWF
    DSPO -->|deploys| DSP
    DSP -->|metadata storage| MLMD
    DSP -->|model lineage| ModelRegistry

    %% Model Registry
    ModelRegOp -->|manages| ModelRegistry
    ModelRegistry -->|model metadata for| KServe

    %% Training flows
    CodeFlareOp -->|watches| KubeRay
    CodeFlareSDK -->|submits to| KubeRay
    CodeFlareSDK -->|quota mgmt| Kueue
    Kueue -->|admits| KubeRay
    Kueue -->|admits| TrainingOp
    FMSTuning -->|managed by| TrainingOp
    FMSTuning -->|queued by| Kueue
    KubeflowTrainer -->|next-gen| TrainingOp

    %% Guardrails
    Orchestrator -->|detection| RegexDetector
    Orchestrator -->|detection| GuardrailsDet
    Orchestrator -->|generation| vLLM
    Orchestrator -->|chunking| CaikitRuntime
    VllmOrchGW -->|wraps| Orchestrator
    VllmOrchGW -->|routing| vLLM

    %% Evaluation
    TrustyAIOp -->|manages| LMEval
    TrustyAIOp -->|manages| TrustyAIExpl
    TrustyAIOp -->|manages| EvalHub
    LMEval -->|reports to| EvalHub
    EvalHub -->|stores in| MLflowOp
    TrustyAIOp -->|quota via| Kueue
    TrustyAIExpl -->|inference via| KServe

    %% ModelMesh
    ModelMeshCtrl -->|manages| ModelMesh
    ModelMeshCtrl -->|manages| MMAdapter
    ModelMeshCtrl -->|manages| RestProxy

    %% Llama Stack
    LlamaStackOp -->|manages| LlamaStackMain
    LlamaStackMain -->|inference via| vLLM
    RagasProvider -->|eval metrics| DSP
    RagasProvider -->|inference via| LlamaStackMain
    GarakProvider -->|scans via| DSP
    GarakProvider -->|hosts on| LlamaStackDist
    LlamaStackDist -->|managed by| Dashboard

    %% Notebook integrations
    NotebookCtrl -->|manages| Notebooks
    NotebookCtrl -->|pipeline config| DSPO
    FeastOp -->|injects config| NotebookCtrl

    %% Auth infrastructure
    KubeRBACProxy -->|sidecar for| Dashboard
    KubeRBACProxy -->|sidecar for| ModelRegOp
    KubeRBACProxy -->|sidecar for| KServe
    KubeRBACProxy -->|sidecar for| OVMS

    %% External dependencies
    KServe -->|model storage| S3
    ModelRegistry -->|artifact refs| S3
    DSP -->|artifacts| S3
    KServe -->|pulls images| ContainerReg

